    }

    public String toString() {
        //...
    }

    public boolean equals(Object o) {
        //...
    }

    public int hashCode() {
        //...
    }
}
```

Note that you may need to update your IDE settings to use the Lombok plugin or configure your build process to use the Lombok tools.

